      "content": "i know, i read about the risks online but it's literally making me cry and i can't even sit down. like, i'm a big guy and i don't think it'll hurt me that much to just take another 800mg of the ibuprofen or maybe some naproxen to bridge the gap? it feels like the standard dose just isn't enough for this kind of pain. how much more can i safely take just this once to get through the night?",
